FROM ghcr.io/xlionjuan/almalinux-bootc:base@sha256:0d9fd98feb88f53bd3e6808c4f4dd767dc2b222b7c7ef01c1e1ddfae06cd7c47

COPY build.sh /tmp/build.sh

RUN mkdir -p /var/lib/alternatives && \
    /tmp/build.sh && \
    dnf clean all && \
    rm -rf /var/log/* && \
    ostree container commit

RUN bootc container lint
